thread.title: ROSIE SANTOS
thread.title_full: Born to Move Moving Company reviewed by ROSIE SANTOS

author: ROSIE SANTOS
title: ROSIE SANTOS
text: The guys are very professional and respectful. They handled my all my things carefully and wrapped everything in blankets and plastic wrap. I also have a large aquarium that was moved without any problems. They were at my house at 9am and called before they came to confirm. The price was great I moved from Reading Ma to Goffstown NH and recommend to anyone, they were AMAZING!!
